                  <td style="padding: 16px;"><strong>Podwójny VPN (multi-hop)</strong></td>
                  <td style="padding: 16px; text-align: center; font-weight: 600;">-50% i więcej</td>
                  <td style="padding: 16px; text-align: center;">
                    <span style="background: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800;">MAX PRYWATNOŚĆ</span>
